{"tid":462761,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母垃圾連登仔敢做唔敢認衰仔","createTime":"2017-11-09T00:47:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-09T02:40:26.000Z","uid":34676,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"499c64028d85e9a911700e3ef29294c9e3f397c6","tid":462761,"uid":34676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T00:47:05.000Z","msg":"次撚次就大大力撞埋去炒車<br />\n新聞一出知道個叔叔咁撚慘<br />\n而且真係唔係賣狗肉<br />\n個個拍下屎忽就走撚咗去<br />\n思古井單野又係咁<br />\n今次又係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n次次有事就大大力落井下石先<br />\n成鳩日屌人帶風向，根本自己先係最易被人帶到風向嗰個<br />\n剩係識將個波射俾何來<br />\n人地講下就信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己有腦，有智慧就唔會受人危言聳聽啦<br />\n屌你老母你地唔單只要去討伐何來呢條撚屌啊<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你地咁中意出嚟m 記聚<br />\n有冇考慮成堆連登仔去仔地阿叔到幫襯聚下咁呢？補返下人地冇咗既收入呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"9c8e16236f1d4970fb23440d600ebe1f54edd732","tid":462761,"uid":78533,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T00:55:09.000Z","msg":"做咩啫你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5198e2fb5507c17d84968916476bdfc1ba1dc2d","tid":462761,"uid":127506,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T00:56:44.000Z","msg":"未慣？"},{"pid":"72c4972f648ebec0f99fb8c1f2e6bc0f9412b294","tid":462761,"uid":34676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T02:22:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>未慣？</blockquote><br />\n慣咗就代表啱咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cedcc7e78b4bbb040c62514d434828e4cb53a0e2","tid":462761,"uid":34444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T02:40:26.000Z","msg":"洗唔洗又特登開個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}